# Scope — Phase 1 only

Governed by @PLAN.md. Do not expand scope without updating that file.

## In scope
- Landing, login, `/auth/callback`, onboarding (5 steps), dashboard
- `profiles` + `wedding_budgets` with RLS; upsert budget keyed by `user_id`
- Venue tiers: cheap / average / premium / custom (prices in `packages/shared/src/venue-pricing.ts`)
- Server data gateway: `POST /api/profiles`, `GET /api/budget`, `PUT /api/budget` (+ system `GET /api/health`, `GET /api/openapi.json`)

## Explicitly out of scope
- Extra budget categories, vendors, marketplace, payments, admin, wedding sites
- Service-role / admin-bypass server endpoints
- Any microservices split beyond `client/`, `server/`, `packages/shared/`

If a request would expand scope, stop and ask.
